title: BwB Battery
content:
I'm modeling the Bean-with-Bacon Megarocket but when making 2d images 3d there often come difficulties.

In Keen 1-6 the bwb has the battery on it's left side...
In Keen GBC it's on the right side...

I asume the right position is on the left like in the original Keen games. Is this just another spoiler or does the bwb have 2 batteries?-------------------------------
AvK - Aliens vs Keen
